  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/data/src/utils/utilities.ts?message=docs(data)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L12-L33\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/15.0.0/modules/data/src/utils/utilities.ts#L12-L33\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/data\", \"name\": \"@ngrx/data\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/data/flattenArgs\", \"name\": \"flattenArgs\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/data\">@ngrx/data</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"flattenargs\">flattenArgs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/data/flattenArgs#flattenargs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Flatten first arg if it is an array\nAllows fn with ...rest signature to be called with an array instead of spread\nExample:</p>\n<code-example>\n// See entity-action-operators.ts\nconst <a href=\"api/data/persistOps\" class=\"code-anchor\">persistOps</a> = [<a href=\"api/data/EntityOp#QUERY_ALL\" class=\"code-anchor\">EntityOp.QUERY_ALL</a>, EntityOp.ADD, ...];\nactions.pipe(<a href=\"api/data/ofEntityOp\" class=\"code-anchor\">ofEntityOp</a>(...persistOps)) // works\nactions.pipe(<a href=\"api/data/ofEntityOp\" class=\"code-anchor\">ofEntityOp</a>(<a href=\"api/data/persistOps\" class=\"code-anchor\">persistOps</a>)) // also works\n</code-example>\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/data/flattenArgs\" class=\"code-anchor\">flattenArgs</a></span>&#x3C;T>(args?: any[]): T[]</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"args\"></a>\n        <code>args</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>any[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>T[]</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/data\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/data\n - api/data/EntityOp#QUERY_ALL\n - api/data/flattenArgs#flattenargs\n - api/data/ofEntityOp\n - api/data/persistOps\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/data/src/utils/utilities.ts?message=docs(data)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L12-L33\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/15.0.0/modules/data/src/utils/utilities.ts#L12-L33\n-->"
